snippet.title: Boycott Aquaman 2 - Amber Heard Is An Abuser! #JusticeForJohnnyDepp
snippet.description:
It sucks to see a man like Johnny Depp lose everything to this liar, abuser, and manipulator Amber Heard. She deserves to lose everything for physically hurting this man. And Warner Bros don't deserve our money so boycott Aquaman 2.
